IMPORTANT NOTE ON PRE-TRAINED CHECKPOINTS:
The pre-trained model checkpoints included in the checkpoints/ directory were
trained using the I-CARE, DEAP, DREAMER, and TUH EEG datasets. Use of these
checkpoints is subject to the data use agreements of the respective datasets.
The checkpoints may only be used for research purposes and only by researchers
who have obtained valid access to the underlying training datasets.
